0 errors | 0 warnings | 0 notes
## Test environments
* Windows 11 x64, R 4.5.1 (local)
## Downstream dependencies
None - this is a new package.
', "cran-comments.md")
system('git add -A')
system('git commit -m "Fix CRAN resubmission: Unicode in Rd files and DESCRIPTION References field"')
